title: Introducing: Comedy Central’s Hell Of A Week with Charlamagne Tha God
itunes:title: Introducing: Comedy Central’s Hell Of A Week with Charlamagne Tha God
description:
Charlamagne Tha God invites unlikely pairings of comedians, outspoken celebrities, and thought-leaders across the political spectrum to debate the current events permeating politics and culture. With each week on fire, this weekly late-night show will feature influential guests unpacking the stories blazing the headlines. Comedy Central’s Hell Of A Week with Charlamagne Tha God is the week's last laugh. Catch new episodes every Friday.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
